title: Converse - Wall to Wall: Austin, TX
description: Austin based artist Josh Row took the vibrant Converse spring color palette and turned it into something wholly his own -- featuring a giraffe with rad sunglasses, a pair of Chucks, and a message that everyone can agree with.
